ance, and client needs. </li><li>Build and manage a portfolio of client opportunities, maintaining accuracy to client needs, and delivering phenomenal solutions that enable our clients' brands to stand out. </li><li>Collaborate with internal merchandising, creative, and fulfillment teams to deliver tailored client solutions that reflect brand identity and achieve clients' marketing goals. </li><li>Serve as a confident industry expert, quickly uncovering opportunities to help our client’s brand thrive through creative, results-driven merchandise strategies. </li><li>Provide leadership on in-region logistics, including supplier partnerships, shipping coordination, and operational needs unique to Dubai. </li><li>Ensure accurate and timely delivery of high-quality promotional products, even under fast-moving and high-pressure timelines—without compromising quality or missing delivery expectations. </li><li>Represent BDA with professionalism and integrity at trade events, client meetings, and industry functions in the region. </li><li>Share insights and data regularly to inform strategic planning and expansion decisions. <br><br></li></ul><strong>Job Skills And Traits That Lead To Success<br><br></strong><ul><li>A strong entrepreneurial spirit—you’re energized by building something from the ground up. </li><li>Client-obsessed mindset—you’re passionate about delivering meaningful branded merchandise solutions that drive business results. </li><li>Skilled in navigating enterprise-level relationships, understanding multiple stakeholders, with the ability to move quickly, identify immediate opportunities, and maintain momentum. </li><li>Culturally attuned and locally connected within the Middle East, with a broad global understanding of delivering outstanding service for client needs. </li><li>A trusted thought leader—you spot trends early, guide creative direction, and inspire client confidence. </li><li>Comfortable working autonomously while staying highly collaborative wi