essionals, these roles ensure that clinical trials are conducted efficiently and effectively, ultimately contributing to the advancement of medical research and the development of new treatments. Core Focus Overseeing the development and coordination of Phase 1 clinical research studies Collaborating with principal investigators and serving as liaisons between various stakeholders Planning logistics and resource usage for clinical trials Tracking study progress in alignment with project milestones, client deliverables, and budget Ensuring compliance with global and regional regulations Contributing to the design, implementation, and delivery of processes, programs, and policies Managing processes and potentially directing the work of lower-level professionals",
